    <main>
        @*Main Content of the Homepage*@
        <aside>@*Consists of the side content that is associated with the bidding system*@
            <h2> Mission </h2> @*Brief description of the mission of the bidding system*@
            <p> The mission of the Eduvos Online Bidding System is to create an innovative, fair, and accessible platform for repurposing retired computer equipment.</p>
        </aside>

        <section>
            @*This is a depandable sub element that is reliant on the context of the website, it consists of the About Us Page, and the How it Works Page*@
            <h2> About Us </h2> @*Briefly describes what the bidding system is about*@
            <p>
                Welcome to Eduvos Online Bidding Experience!

                Are you looking for excellent tech deals? Look no further! Eduvos is excited to launch its Online Bidding System, a dynamic platform where you may bid, win, and save on high-quality used computer equipment.

                We believe in giving technology a second chance while making it available to those that require it the most. Our open and exciting auction system enables Eduvos to offer available equipment with a starting bid price, allowing clients like you to compete for the best prices in real time.
            </p>
        </section>

        <article>@*Represents the dependent and independent content of the bidding system*@
            <h2> How it Works ? </h2> @*Detailed explaination on how the bidding system works*@
            <p>
                Browse and bid on available computer equipment.

                Watch as prices update in real-time—if multiple bids come in, you'll always see the most recent price.

                Get fantastic deals on trustworthy technology!

                Whether you're a student seeking affordable devices or a business seeking cost-effective tech solutions, Eduvos is here to help you find the gear you need at the best price.

                Join the auction, place a bid, and win big on high-end computer equipment!
            </p>
        </article>

